Story #55 (My Day Auto-Add) is complete. There are 3 more stories with `passes: false` (#56, #57, #58). Exiting normally for the next call.

**Summary of what was built:**
- **Migration**: Added `my_day_dismissed_date` column to tasks table (SQLite migration_16 + Supabase migration)
- **Auto-add logic**: `autoAddMyDayTasks()` in TaskRepository — runs on My Day hydrate, respects mode (off/due_today/due_today_or_overdue), skips subtasks/done/archived/dismissed tasks
- **Simplified findMyDay()**: Both SQLite and Supabase repos now only check `is_in_my_day = 1` (removed dual filter hack)
- **Dismissed date handling**: Context menus, bulk menus, and TaskRow all set `my_day_dismissed_date` when removing from My Day
- **Settings UI**: Auto-add dropdown + re-add dismissed toggle in Settings > Projects > My Day
- **Telegram bot**: `/myday` now returns pinned + due/overdue tasks, sorted by due date
- **Sync**: `my_day_dismissed_date` synced via PersonalSyncService push/pull
- **Tests**: 14 new tests covering all auto-add edge cases + findMyDay simplification
